                        <interp inst="t18471025-name-342" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN JENKINSON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, G</hi> 53.) I took Cox at the Bald-faced Stag—he said he knew nothing about it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cox's Defence.</hi> There is a free passage to the cellar where this watch was found; anybody could go there.</p>
